original_title: Final Curtain: Part 10 - The Terror Lives On
overview: Ethan Carver lives on. He is hiding out in the woods at Emerald Lake, watching silently as a group of campers spends a carefree weekend. One by one, Ethan stalks and kills them. With no shelter, no communications and no transportation, the campers are all alone, facing off against an unstoppable murderer.
title: Final Curtain: Part 10 - The Terror Lives On
